  "response": "There are several institutions in Delhi that offer Teradata training. Here are some options you might consider:\n\n1. **NIIT**: NIIT offers various courses in data warehousing and database management, which may include training in Teradata as part of their curriculum.\n\n2. **Intellipaat**: This online training platform often provides courses on Teradata along with practical projects and assignments.\n\n3. **Cromacampus**: They offer specialized training in data warehousing, including Teradata concepts.\n\n4. **Edureka**: Edureka provides live instructor-led classes on a variety of subjects, including Teradata, focusing on hands-on experience.\n\n5. **Online Training Platforms**: Websites like Udemy, Coursera, and LinkedIn Learning also feature courses on Teradata that can be taken at your own pace.\n\n6. **Local Institutes**: You can also check local engineering or computer science training institutes in Delhi that have courses on data warehousing technologies.\n\nMake sure to verify the credentials of the institute, check reviews from past students, and see if they provide hands-on training and real-world projects.",
